data.description:
Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Greenwood, AR! This beautifully remodeled residence seamlessly blends modern elegance with classic charm, offering a perfect balance for contemporary living.Step into the open-concept living space, where natural light floods through large windows, highlighting the stunning vinyl floors that flow throughout. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring top-of-the-line appliances, quartz countertops, and a stylish tile backsplash. Imagine hosting gatherings in the spacious dining area, creating lasting memories with family and friends.Adjacent to the living area, discover a versatile flex space that can easily be transformed into an office or playroom, providing the perfect solution for your dynamic lifestyle. This additional space offers endless possibilities to suit your family's needs.
Retreat to the master suite, a tranquil haven boasting a spa-like ensuite bath and ample closet space. The additional bedrooms are thoughtfully designed, providing comfort and versatility for any lifestyle.Indulge in outdoor living on the expansive patio, perfect for al fresco dining or simply unwinding while enjoying the lush surroundings. Conveniently located in a desirable neighborhood, this home is within close proximity to schools, parks, and local amenities. With its impeccable craftsmanship, modern amenities, and flexible living spaces, this remodeled gem in Greenwood, AR, is ready to welcome you home. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your forever home. Outbuilding does not convey.
